<br>
Without necro dumps and a bard twisting songs with PT you are asking for slack damage. Sounds like you are missing POTG also, all of which make a TON of difference and typically (in our raids at least) are always there for the wizzies.<br>
<br>
Add POTG and bard song and try it again and I bet the results will greater differ.  Necro dumping you would of course blow you over the top but thats would not make it fair on your end.<br>
